Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.15,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.15,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,今日はここでお昼を食べましょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:08.00,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:08.00,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,エントランスの休憩スペースかぁ～。\n新鮮でいいね！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.25,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.25,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,あ、あそこのテーブルあいてるよ！\n確保～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:19.81,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:19.81,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,わぁ～！　お姉ちゃんが作ってくれた\nお弁当、今日も美味しそうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:25.56,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:25.56,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,ふっふっふ～。まわりの意見を\n聞いて、見映えを改良したことで、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:30.51,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:30.51,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,見た目も味も栄養も！\n完璧なものに進化したわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:33.74,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:33.74,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,ほんとだ。\nペーストじゃ、なくなってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.35,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.35,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,うわぁ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.92,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.92,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,あ、広ちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.88,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.88,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,び、びっくりしたぁ～～～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.79,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.79,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,さぷらーいず。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:45.14,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:45.14,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,わたしも、お昼、いっしょにいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.29,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.29,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,もっちろん！\nいいよね？　お姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.69,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.69,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,ええ。歓迎するわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.28,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.28,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,…………
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.77,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.77,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,進化した咲季のお弁当、気になる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:58.96,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:58.96,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,一口、ちょうだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:02.41,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:02.41,Campus Common,咲季,0,0,0,,いいわよ。\nほら、そこに座りなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:07.16,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:07.16,Campus Common,広,0,0,0,,やさしい。\nお姉ちゃん…………好き。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:11.65,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:11.65,Campus Common,佑芽,0,0,0,,広ちゃん！？　お姉ちゃんは\nあたしのお姉ちゃんだよ！？！？
